Detailed Description

The class represents a CONNECT message. The message has the following structure: <xmp> struct Connect { struct IPDRStreamingHeader header; int initiatorAddress; short initiatorPort; int capabilities; // an array of capability bits for capability negotiation int keepAliveInterval; // the maximum delay between some indication from remote, in seconds UTF8String vendorId; // the vendor ID of Exporter/Collector } </xmp>
